  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\n@guybrush points out that web3signer has an endpoint like `/api/v1/eth2/publicKey` for fetching the list of available validators.\r\n\r\nThe Lighthouse VC could (optionally) poll this endpoint to auto-enable validators.\r\n",
